data.description: Welcome to this lovely 4 bedroom, 2 bath, one story gem.   Home still looks like it is a new construction building with recent new paint and carpeting throughout.  The kitchen boasts a recently purchased electric oven.  If you prefer a gas range, a gas fitting is available.  Stainless steel appliances include a microwave and dishwasher.  Refrigerator is NOT included.  Located near schools, shops and convenience stores.  Make an appointment today!
